---
title: Tenderloin Steaks and Bacon-Wrapped Green Beans  with Creamy Garlic Mash
description: Bacon-wrapped green beans, need we say more? This pan-seared steak gets the royal treatment with creamy garlic mash and horseradish aioli. Treat your loved ones to the perfect steak night!

